        <ontology:usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology xml:lang="es">Co-construcción con expertos del dominio y alineación iterativa con ontologías de referencia</ontology:usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology>
        <ontology:usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology xml:lang="fr">Co-construction avec des experts métier et alignement itératif avec des ontologies de référence</ontology:usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology>
        <ontology:usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology xml:lang="en">Co-construction with domain experts and iterative alignment with reference ontologies</ontology:usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology>
        <ontology:usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology xml:lang="ro">Co-construcție cu experți din domeniu și aliniere iterativă cu ontologii de referință</ontology:usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology>
        <ontology:usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology xml:lang="pt">Co-construção com especialistas no domínio e alinhamento iterativo com ontologias de referência</ontology:usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology>
        <ontology:usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology xml:lang="it">Co-costruzione con esperti di dominio e allineamento iterativo con ontologie di riferimento</ontology:usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology>
