        <ontology:version>1.0.0</ontology:version>
        <terms:abstract xml:lang="pt">A ontologia OSO estrutura os observatórios marinhos em três níveis hierárquicos: infraestruturas regionais, locais e plataformas. Suporta a gestão FAIR de dados, a interoperabilidade e a integração de informações sobre infraestruturas marinhas, especialmente no contexto do EMSO ERIC.</terms:abstract>
        <terms:abstract xml:lang="it">L&apos;ontologia OSO struttura gli osservatori marini in tre livelli gerarchici: infrastrutture regionali, siti e piattaforme. Supporta la gestione FAIR dei dati, l&apos;interoperabilità e l&apos;integrazione delle informazioni sulle infrastrutture marine, in particolare nel contesto EMSO ERIC.</terms:abstract>
        <terms:abstract xml:lang="fr">L&apos;ontologie OSO structure les observatoires marins en trois niveaux hiérarchiques : infrastructures régionales, sites et plateformes. Elle soutient la gestion FAIR des données, l&apos;interopérabilité et l&apos;intégration des informations sur les infrastructures marines, notamment dans le cadre d&apos;EMSO ERIC.</terms:abstract>
        <terms:abstract xml:lang="es">La ontología OSO estructura los observatorios marinos en tres niveles jerárquicos: infraestructuras regionales, sitios y plataformas. Apoya la gestión FAIR de datos, la interoperabilidad y la integración de información sobre infraestructuras marinas, especialmente en el contexto de EMSO ERIC.</terms:abstract>
        <terms:abstract xml:lang="no">OSO-ontologien strukturerer marine observatorier i tre hierarkiske nivåer: regionale fasiliteter, steder og plattformer. Den støtter FAIR datastyring, interoperabilitet og integrasjon av informasjon om marine infrastrukturer, spesielt i EMSO ERIC-konteksten.</terms:abstract>
        <terms:abstract xml:lang="ro">Ontologia OSO structurează observatoarele marine în trei niveluri ierarhice: facilități regionale, situri și platforme. Susține gestionarea FAIR a datelor, interoperabilitatea și integrarea informațiilor despre infrastructuri marine, în special în contextul EMSO ERIC.</terms:abstract>
        <terms:abstract xml:lang="en">The OSO ontology structures marine observatories into three hierarchical levels: Regional Facilities, Sites, and Platforms. It supports FAIR data management, interoperability, and integration of heterogeneous marine infrastructure information, particularly within the EMSO ERIC framework.</terms:abstract>
        <terms:abstract xml:lang="el">Η οντολογία OSO οργανώνει τα θαλάσσια παρατηρητήρια σε τρία ιεραρχικά επίπεδα: περιφερειακές υποδομές, τοποθεσίες και πλατφόρμες. Υποστηρίζει τη διαχείριση δεδομένων σύμφωνα με τις αρχές FAIR, τη διαλειτουργικότητα και την ενσωμάτωση πληροφοριών για θαλάσσιες υποδομές, ιδιαίτερα στο πλαίσιο του EMSO ERIC.</terms:abstract>
        <terms:bibliographicCitation xml:lang="en">OSO – Observatories of the Seas Ontology (OSO). Version 1.0.0. EMSO ERIC / Ifremer. FAIRsharing DOI: 10.25504/FAIRsharing.654931.</terms:bibliographicCitation>
