        <schema:codeRepository rdf:resource="https://github.com/emso-eric/oso-ontology"/>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="no">Ontologi som beskriver forholdet mellom regionale fasiliteter, steder, plattformer, forskningsinfrastrukturer, organisasjoner, cruiser og de ansvarlige på hvert nivå.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="it">Ontologia che descrive le relazioni tra strutture regionali, siti, piattaforme, infrastrutture di ricerca, organizzazioni, crociere e i responsabili di ciascun livello.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="pt">Ontologia que descreve as relações entre instalações regionais, locais, plataformas, infraestruturas de investigação, organizações, cruzeiros e os responsáveis por cada nível.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="ro">Ontologie care descrie relațiile dintre facilitățile regionale, siturile, platformele, infrastructurile de cercetare, organizațiile, croazierele și persoanele responsabile la fiecare nivel.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="fr">Ontologie décrivant les relations entre les nœuds régionaux, les sites, les plateformes, les infrastructures de recherche, les organisations, les campagnes à la mer et les personnes responsables à chaque niveau.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Ontology describing the relationships between Regional Facilities, Sites, Platforms, Research Infrastructures, Organisations, Cruises, and the persons in charge of each level.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="es">Ontología que describe las relaciones entre instalaciones regionales, emplazamientos, plataformas, infraestructuras de investigación, organizaciones, cruceros y las personas responsables de cada nivel.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="el">Οντολογία που περιγράφει τις σχέσεις μεταξύ περιφερειακών υποδομών, τοποθεσιών, πλατφορμών, ερευνητικών υποδομών, οργανισμών, αποστολών και των υπευθύνων σε κάθε επίπεδο.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">Observatories of the Seas Ontology (OSO)</rdfs:label>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="no">Ontologi for marine observatorier (OSO)</rdfs:label>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="it">Ontologia degli osservatori marini (OSO)</rdfs:label>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="pt">Ontologia dos observatórios marinhos (OSO)</rdfs:label>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="ro">Ontologia observatoarelor marine (OSO)</rdfs:label>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="fr">Ontologie des observatoires marins (OSO)</rdfs:label>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="es">Ontología de los observatorios marinos (OSO)</rdfs:label>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="el">Οντολογία θαλάσσιων παρατηρητηρίων (OSO)</rdfs:label>
        <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:resource="https://emso-eric.github.io/oso-ontology/"/>
        <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:resource="https://fairsharing.org/FAIRsharing.654931"/>
        <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:resource="https://github.com/emso-eric/oso-ontology"/>
        <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:resource="https://service.tib.eu/webvowl/#iri=https://earthportal.eu/ontologies/OSO"/>
        <versionInfo xml:lang="en">1.0.0 - First stable public release</versionInfo>
        <skos:altLabel>OSO</skos:altLabel>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="ro">Această ontologie are ca scop descrierea observatoarelor subacvatice, în special a celor asociate cu Observatoarele multidisciplinare europene ale fundului mării și coloanei de apă (EMSO), care constituie un consorțiu european de infrastructură de cercetare (ERIC) din 2016.</skos:definition>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="fr">Cette ontologie vise à décrire les observatoires sous-marins, en particulier ceux associés au réseau européen d&apos;observatoires multidisciplinaires des fonds marins et de la colonne d&apos;eau (EMSO), qui constitue un consortium européen d&apos;infrastructures de recherche (ERIC) depuis 2016.</skos:definition>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="no">Denne ontologien har som mål å beskrive undervannsobservatorier, særlig de som er tilknyttet European Multidisciplinary Seafloor and Water Column Observatories (EMSO), som har vært et europeisk forskningsinfrastrukturkonsortium (ERIC) siden 2016.</skos:definition>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="pt">Esta ontologia visa descrever observatórios subaquáticos, em particular os associados ao Observatório Multidisciplinar Europeu do Fundo Marinho e da Coluna de Água (EMSO), que é um Consórcio Europeu de Infraestruturas de Investigação (ERIC) desde 2016.</skos:definition>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="es">Esta ontología tiene como objetivo describir los observatorios submarinos, en particular los asociados al Observatorio Multidisciplinar Europeo del Fondo Marino y la Columna de Agua (EMSO), que es un Consorcio Europeo de Infraestructuras de Investigación (ERIC) desde 2016.</skos:definition>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="it">Questa ontologia ha lo scopo di descrivere gli osservatori sottomarini, in particolare quelli associati agli Osservatori multidisciplinari europei dei fondali marini e della colonna d&apos;acqua (EMSO), che dal 2016 costituiscono un Consorzio europeo per le infrastrutture di ricerca (ERIC).</skos:definition>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This ontology aims to describe underwater observatories, in particular those associated with the European Multidisciplinary Seafloor and Water Column Observatories (EMSO), which has been a European Research Infrastructure Consortium (ERIC) since 2016.</skos:definition>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="el">Η οντολογία αυτή έχει ως στόχο να περιγράψει τα υποβρύχια παρατηρητήρια, ιδίως εκείνα που συνδέονται με τα Ευρωπαϊκά Πολυεπιστημονικά Παρατηρητήρια Θαλάσσιου Βυθού και Υδροκολώνας (EMSO), τα οποία αποτελούν Ευρωπαϊκό Συνεταιρισμό Ερευνητικής Υποδομής (ERIC) από το 2016.</skos:definition>
        <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Observatories of the Seas Ontology</skos:prefLabel>
