    <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#hasEDMO">
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="ro">Această proprietate leagă o organizație de identificatorul său EDMO (European Directory of Marine Organisations).</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="fr">Cette propriété relie une organisation à son identifiant EDMO (European Directory of Marine Organisations).</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="no">Denne egenskapen kobler en organisasjon til dens EDMO-identifikator (European Directory of Marine Organisations).</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="es">Esta propiedad vincula una Organización con su identificador EDMO (European Directory of Marine Organisations).</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="pt">Esta propriedade liga uma Organização ao seu identificador EDMO (European Directory of Marine Organisations).</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="it">Questa proprietà collega un&apos;Organizzazione al suo identificatore EDMO (European Directory of Marine Organisations).</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">This property links an Organisation to its EDMO (European Directory of Marine Organisations) identifier.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="el">Αυτή η ιδιότητα συνδέει έναν Οργανισμό με το αναγνωριστικό EDMO (European Directory of Marine Organisations).</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="fr">a un EDMO</rdfs:label>
